    <description>
      <p>The holder of this item gains:
        <ul>
          <li><b>Githborn Psionic Weapon:</b> When wielded by a githyanki this weapon deals an additional 1d6 Psychic damage.</li>
          <li><b>Githborn Psionic Resistance:</b> A githyanki holding this weapon has Advantage of Intelligence, Wisdom, and Charisma saving throws, resistance to Psychic damage, and cannot be Charmed.</li>
        </ul>
      </p>       
    <setters>
